{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Embracing otherness."},{"time":3000,"text":"When I first heard this theme,"},{"time":5000,"text":"I thought, well, embracing otherness"},{"time":7000,"text":"is embracing myself."},{"time":10000,"text":"And the journey to that place"},{"time":12000,"text":"of understanding and acceptance"},{"time":14000,"text":"has been an interesting one for me,"},{"time":17000,"text":"and it's given me an insight"},{"time":19000,"text":"into the whole notion of self,"},{"time":21000,"text":"which I think is worth sharing with you today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"We each have a self,"},{"time":27000,"text":"but I don't think that we're born with one."},{"time":30000,"text":"You know how newborn babies"},{"time":32000,"text":"believe they're part of everything;"},{"time":34000,"text":"they're not separate?"},{"time":36000,"text":"Well that fundamental sense of oneness"},{"time":39000,"text":"is lost on us very quickly."},{"time":41000,"text":"It's like that initial stage is over --"},{"time":43000,"text":"oneness: infancy,"},{"time":45000,"text":"unformed, primitive."},{"time":47000,"text":"It's no longer valid or real."},{"time":50000,"text":"What is real is separateness,"},{"time":52000,"text":"and at some point in early babyhood,"},{"time":54000,"text":"the idea of self"},{"time":56000,"text":"starts to form."},{"time":58000,"text":"Our little portion of oneness is given a name,"},{"time":61000,"text":"is told all kinds of things about itself,"},{"time":64000,"text":"and these details,"},{"time":66000,"text":"opinions and ideas"},{"time":68000,"text":"become facts,"},{"time":70000,"text":"which go towards building ourselves,"},{"time":72000,"text":"our identity."},{"time":74000,"text":"And that self becomes the vehicle"},{"time":76000,"text":"for navigating our social world."},{"time":79000,"text":"But the self is a projection"},{"time":82000,"text":"based on other people's projections."},{"time":84000,"text":"Is it who we really are?"},{"time":87000,"text":"Or who we really want to be, or should be?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"So this whole interaction"},{"time":93000,"text":"with self and identity"},{"time":95000,"text":"was a very difficult one for me growing up."},{"time":97000,"text":"The self that I attempted to take out into the world"},{"time":100000,"text":"was rejected over and over again."},{"time":103000,"text":"And my panic"},{"time":105000,"text":"at not having a self that fit,"},{"time":107000,"text":"and the confusion that came"},{"time":109000,"text":"from my self being rejected,"},{"time":111000,"text":"created anxiety, shame"},{"time":114000,"text":"and hopelessness,"},{"time":116000,"text":"which kind of defined me for a long time."},{"time":119000,"text":"But in retrospect,"},{"time":121000,"text":"the destruction of my self was so repetitive"},{"time":124000,"text":"that I started to see a pattern."},{"time":126000,"text":"The self changed,"},{"time":129000,"text":"got affected, broken, destroyed,"},{"time":132000,"text":"but another one would evolve --"},{"time":135000,"text":"sometimes stronger,"},{"time":137000,"text":"sometimes hateful,"},{"time":139000,"text":"sometimes not wanting to be there at all."},{"time":141000,"text":"The self was not constant."},{"time":145000,"text":"And how many times"},{"time":147000,"text":"would my self have to die"},{"time":149000,"text":"before I realized"},{"time":151000,"text":"that it was never alive in the first place?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":154000,"text":"I grew up on the coast of England"},{"time":156000,"text":"in the '70s."},{"time":158000,"text":"My dad is white from Cornwall,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and my mom is black from Zimbabwe."},{"time":165000,"text":"Even the idea of us as a family"},{"time":167000,"text":"was challenging to most people."},{"time":170000,"text":"But nature had its wicked way,"},{"time":172000,"text":"and brown babies were born."},{"time":174000,"text":"But from about the age of five,"},{"time":176000,"text":"I was aware that I didn't fit."},{"time":179000,"text":"I was the black atheist kid"},{"time":182000,"text":"in the all-white Catholic school run by nuns."},{"time":185000,"text":"I was an anomaly,"},{"time":187000,"text":"and my self was rooting around for definition"},{"time":191000,"text":"and trying to plug in."},{"time":194000,"text":"Because the self likes to fit,"},{"time":196000,"text":"to see itself replicated,"},{"time":198000,"text":"to belong."},{"time":200000,"text":"That confirms its existence"},{"time":202000,"text":"and its importance."},{"time":204000,"text":"And it is important."},{"time":206000,"text":"It has an extremely important function."},{"time":208000,"text":"Without it, we literally can't interface with others."},{"time":212000,"text":"We can't hatch plans"},{"time":214000,"text":"and climb that stairway of popularity,"},{"time":217000,"text":"of success."},{"time":219000,"text":"But my skin color wasn't right."},{"time":222000,"text":"My hair wasn't right."},{"time":224000,"text":"My history wasn't right."},{"time":226000,"text":"My self became defined"},{"time":228000,"text":"by otherness,"},{"time":230000,"text":"which meant that, in that social world,"},{"time":232000,"text":"I didn't really exist."},{"time":234000,"text":"And I was \"other\" before being anything else --"},{"time":237000,"text":"even before being a girl."},{"time":240000,"text":"I was a noticeable nobody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"Another world was opening up"},{"time":246000,"text":"around this time:"},{"time":248000,"text":"performance and dancing."},{"time":251000,"text":"That nagging dread of self-hood"},{"time":254000,"text":"didn't exist when I was dancing."},{"time":257000,"text":"I'd literally lose myself."},{"time":260000,"text":"And I was a really good dancer."},{"time":263000,"text":"I would put"},{"time":265000,"text":"all my emotional expression"},{"time":267000,"text":"into my dancing."},{"time":269000,"text":"I could be in the movement"},{"time":272000,"text":"in a way that I wasn't able to be"},{"time":274000,"text":"in my real life, in myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"And at 16,"},{"time":279000,"text":"I stumbled across another opportunity,"},{"time":282000,"text":"and I earned my first acting role in a film."},{"time":286000,"text":"I can hardly find the words"},{"time":288000,"text":"to describe the peace I felt"},{"time":291000,"text":"when I was acting."},{"time":293000,"text":"My dysfunctional self"},{"time":295000,"text":"could actually plug in"},{"time":297000,"text":"to another self, not my own,"},{"time":299000,"text":"and it felt so good."},{"time":302000,"text":"It was the first time that I existed"},{"time":304000,"text":"inside a fully-functioning self --"},{"time":307000,"text":"one that I controlled,"},{"time":310000,"text":"that I steered,"},{"time":312000,"text":"that I gave life to."},{"time":315000,"text":"But the shooting day would end,"},{"time":317000,"text":"and I'd return"},{"time":319000,"text":"to my gnarly, awkward self."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322000,"text":"By 19,"},{"time":325000,"text":"I was a fully-fledged movie actor,"},{"time":327000,"text":"but still searching for definition."},{"time":330000,"text":"I applied to read anthropology"},{"time":332000,"text":"at university."},{"time":334000,"text":"Dr. Phyllis Lee gave me my interview,"},{"time":337000,"text":"and she asked me, \"How would you define race?\""},{"time":341000,"text":"Well, I thought I had the answer to that one,"},{"time":343000,"text":"and I said, \"Skin color.\""},{"time":346000,"text":"\"So biology, genetics?\" she said."},{"time":350000,"text":"\"Because, Thandie, that's not accurate."},{"time":352000,"text":"Because there's actually more genetic difference"},{"time":355000,"text":"between a black Kenyan"},{"time":357000,"text":"and a black Ugandan"},{"time":359000,"text":"than there is between a black Kenyan"},{"time":362000,"text":"and, say, a white Norwegian."},{"time":364000,"text":"Because we all stem from Africa."},{"time":366000,"text":"So in Africa,"},{"time":368000,"text":"there's been more time"},{"time":370000,"text":"to create genetic diversity.\""},{"time":372000,"text":"In other words,"},{"time":374000,"text":"race has no basis"},{"time":376000,"text":"in biological or scientific fact."},{"time":379000,"text":"On the one hand, result."},{"time":382000,"text":"Right?"},{"time":384000,"text":"On the other hand, my definition of self"},{"time":387000,"text":"just lost a huge chunk of its credibility."},{"time":390000,"text":"But what was credible,"},{"time":392000,"text":"what is biological and scientific fact,"},{"time":395000,"text":"is that we all stem from Africa --"},{"time":398000,"text":"in fact, from a woman called Mitochondrial Eve"},{"time":401000,"text":"who lived 160,000 years ago."},{"time":404000,"text":"And race is an illegitimate concept"},{"time":407000,"text":"which our selves have created"},{"time":409000,"text":"based on fear and ignorance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413000,"text":"Strangely, these revelations"},{"time":415000,"text":"didn't cure my low self-esteem,"},{"time":418000,"text":"that feeling of otherness."},{"time":421000,"text":"My desire to disappear"},{"time":423000,"text":"was still very powerful."},{"time":425000,"text":"I had a degree from Cambridge;"},{"time":427000,"text":"I had a thriving career,"},{"time":429000,"text":"but my self was a car crash,"},{"time":432000,"text":"and I wound up with bulimia"},{"time":434000,"text":"and on a therapist's couch."},{"time":436000,"text":"And of course I did."},{"time":438000,"text":"I still believed"},{"time":440000,"text":"my self was all I was."},{"time":442000,"text":"I still valued self-worth"},{"time":444000,"text":"above all other worth,"},{"time":446000,"text":"and what was there to suggest otherwise?"},{"time":449000,"text":"We've created entire value systems"},{"time":451000,"text":"and a physical reality"},{"time":453000,"text":"to support the worth of self."},{"time":455000,"text":"Look at the industry for self-image"},{"time":457000,"text":"and the jobs it creates,"},{"time":459000,"text":"the revenue it turns over."},{"time":462000,"text":"We'd be right in assuming"},{"time":464000,"text":"that the self is an actual living thing."},{"time":466000,"text":"But it's not. It's a projection"},{"time":469000,"text":"which our clever brains create"},{"time":471000,"text":"in order to cheat ourselves"},{"time":473000,"text":"from the reality of death."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477000,"text":"But there is something"},{"time":479000,"text":"that can give the self"},{"time":481000,"text":"ultimate and infinite connection --"},{"time":484000,"text":"and that thing is oneness,"},{"time":486000,"text":"our essence."},{"time":488000,"text":"The self's struggle"},{"time":490000,"text":"for authenticity and definition"},{"time":492000,"text":"will never end"},{"time":494000,"text":"unless it's connected to its creator --"},{"time":496000,"text":"to you and to me."},{"time":499000,"text":"And that can happen with awareness --"},{"time":502000,"text":"awareness of the reality of oneness"},{"time":505000,"text":"and the projection of self-hood."},{"time":508000,"text":"For a start, we can think about"},{"time":510000,"text":"all the times when we do lose ourselves."},{"time":513000,"text":"It happens when I dance,"},{"time":515000,"text":"when I'm acting."},{"time":517000,"text":"I'm earthed in my essence,"},{"time":519000,"text":"and my self is suspended."},{"time":522000,"text":"In those moments,"},{"time":524000,"text":"I'm connected to everything --"},{"time":526000,"text":"the ground, the air,"},{"time":529000,"text":"the sounds, the energy from the audience."},{"time":531000,"text":"All my senses are alert and alive"},{"time":535000,"text":"in much the same way as an infant might feel --"},{"time":538000,"text":"that feeling of oneness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541000,"text":"And when I'm acting a role,"},{"time":544000,"text":"I inhabit another self,"},{"time":546000,"text":"and I give it life for awhile,"},{"time":548000,"text":"because when the self is suspended"},{"time":551000,"text":"so is divisiveness"},{"time":553000,"text":"and judgment."},{"time":555000,"text":"And I've played everything"},{"time":557000,"text":"from a vengeful ghost in the time of slavery"},{"time":559000,"text":"to Secretary of State in 2004."},{"time":563000,"text":"And no matter how other"},{"time":565000,"text":"these selves might be,"},{"time":567000,"text":"they're all related in me."},{"time":571000,"text":"And I honestly believe"},{"time":573000,"text":"the key to my success as an actor"},{"time":575000,"text":"and my progress as a person"},{"time":577000,"text":"has been the very lack of self"},{"time":580000,"text":"that used to make me feel"},{"time":582000,"text":"so anxious and insecure."},{"time":584000,"text":"I always wondered"},{"time":586000,"text":"why I could feel others' pain so deeply,"},{"time":590000,"text":"why I could recognize"},{"time":592000,"text":"the somebody in the nobody."},{"time":595000,"text":"It's because I didn't have a self to get in the way."},{"time":599000,"text":"I thought I lacked substance,"},{"time":602000,"text":"and the fact that I could feel others'"},{"time":604000,"text":"meant that I had nothing of myself to feel."},{"time":607000,"text":"The thing that was a source of shame"},{"time":610000,"text":"was actually a source of enlightenment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613000,"text":"And when I realized"},{"time":615000,"text":"and really understood"},{"time":617000,"text":"that my self is a projection and that it has a function,"},{"time":620000,"text":"a funny thing happened."},{"time":622000,"text":"I stopped giving it so much authority."},{"time":624000,"text":"I give it its due."},{"time":626000,"text":"I take it to therapy."},{"time":628000,"text":"I've become very familiar"},{"time":630000,"text":"with its dysfunctional behavior."},{"time":632000,"text":"But I'm not ashamed of my self."},{"time":635000,"text":"In fact, I respect my self"},{"time":637000,"text":"and its function."},{"time":639000,"text":"And over time and with practice,"},{"time":642000,"text":"I've tried to live"},{"time":644000,"text":"more and more from my essence."},{"time":646000,"text":"And if you can do that,"},{"time":649000,"text":"incredible things happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651000,"text":"I was in Congo in February,"},{"time":654000,"text":"dancing and celebrating"},{"time":656000,"text":"with women who've survived"},{"time":658000,"text":"the destruction of their selves"},{"time":660000,"text":"in literally unthinkable ways --"},{"time":663000,"text":"destroyed because other brutalized, psychopathic selves"},{"time":666000,"text":"all over that beautiful land"},{"time":669000,"text":"are fueling our selves' addiction"},{"time":672000,"text":"to iPods, Pads, and bling,"},{"time":675000,"text":"which further disconnect ourselves"},{"time":677000,"text":"from ever feeling their pain,"},{"time":679000,"text":"their suffering,"},{"time":681000,"text":"their death."},{"time":683000,"text":"Because, hey,"},{"time":685000,"text":"if we're all living in ourselves"},{"time":687000,"text":"and mistaking it for life,"},{"time":689000,"text":"then we're devaluing"},{"time":691000,"text":"and desensitizing life."},{"time":693000,"text":"And in that disconnected state,"},{"time":695000,"text":"yeah, we can build factory farms with no windows,"},{"time":699000,"text":"destroy marine life"},{"time":701000,"text":"and use rape as a weapon of war."},{"time":705000,"text":"So here's a note to self:"},{"time":708000,"text":"The cracks have started to show"},{"time":710000,"text":"in our constructed world,"},{"time":713000,"text":"and oceans will continue"},{"time":715000,"text":"to surge through the cracks,"},{"time":717000,"text":"and oil and blood,"},{"time":720000,"text":"rivers of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723000,"text":"Crucially, we haven't been figuring out"},{"time":725000,"text":"how to live in oneness"},{"time":727000,"text":"with the Earth and every other living thing."},{"time":730000,"text":"We've just been insanely trying to figure out"},{"time":733000,"text":"how to live with each other -- billions of each other."},{"time":736000,"text":"Only we're not living with each other;"},{"time":738000,"text":"our crazy selves are living with each other"},{"time":741000,"text":"and perpetuating an epidemic"},{"time":743000,"text":"of disconnection."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746000,"text":"Let's live with each other"},{"time":749000,"text":"and take it a breath at a time."},{"time":752000,"text":"If we can get under that heavy self,"},{"time":756000,"text":"light a torch of awareness,"},{"time":758000,"text":"and find our essence,"},{"time":760000,"text":"our connection to the infinite"},{"time":762000,"text":"and every other living thing."},{"time":765000,"text":"We knew it from the day we were born."},{"time":767000,"text":"Let's not be freaked out"},{"time":769000,"text":"by our bountiful nothingness."},{"time":772000,"text":"It's more a reality"},{"time":774000,"text":"than the ones our selves have created."},{"time":776000,"text":"Imagine what kind of existence we can have"},{"time":780000,"text":"if we honor inevitable death of self,"},{"time":784000,"text":"appreciate the privilege of life"},{"time":788000,"text":"and marvel at what comes next."},{"time":792000,"text":"Simple awareness is where it begins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":795000,"text":"Thank you for listening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":797000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}